Plot: Mulder, back on the X-Files but alone for the first time, investigates a series of vampire-like murders in Los Angeles and finds himself falling for the one woman that may be the prime suspect.
Writer: Chris Ruppenthal, Glen Morgan, James Wong
GuestStars: Frank Ferrucci, Tom McBeath, Gustavo Moreno, Justina Vail, Malcolm Stewart, Ken Kramer, Roger Allford, Richard Yee, John Tierney, David Livingstone, Guyle Frazier, Perrey Reeves, Frank Military, Brad Loree
